        <dialogReference>&lt;p&gt;Maximum Angle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Floating point&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Minimum: 0.000000&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maximum: 180.000000&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Default: 30.000000&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maximum angular difference as degree between adjacent segment points.&lt;/p&gt;</dialogReference>
